Manage multiple CDISCDataConnector, CDISCDatasetConnector and CDISCDataset objects.

CDISCData.Rd

Class manages CDISCDataConnector, CDISCDatasetConnector and CDISCDataset objects and aggregate them in one collection. Class also decides whether to launch app before initialize teal application.

Method new()

Create a new object of CDISCData class

Usage

CDISCData$new(..., check = FALSE, join_keys)

Arguments

...

(RelationalDataConnector, Dataset or DatasetConnector) elements to include where ADSL data is mandatory.

check

(logical) reproducibility check - whether evaluated preprocessing code gives the same objects as provided in arguments. Check is run only if flag is true and preprocessing code is not empty.

join_keys

(JoinKeys) or a single (JoinKeySet)
(optional) object with datasets column names used for joining. If empty then it would be automatically derived basing on intersection of datasets primary keys

Method get_parent()

Get all datasets parent names

Usage

CDISCData$get_parent()

Returns

(named list) with dataset name and its corresponding parent dataset name
